\n<div class=\"frame_inner js-home-equalHeight_frame-content\">\n<p class=\"frame_tel\"><a href=\"tel:05017806000\">050-1780-6000</a>（代）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"home-button js-home-equalHeight_button\">\n<li><a href=\"https://mdh.fm/e?kA6036TLRp\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"a-blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span>札幌店専用お問い合わせフォーム</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"column_col\">\n<div class=\"toggle_frame\">\n<h4 class=\"frame_heading js-home-equalHeight_frame-heading\">下関店</h4>\n<div class=\"frame_inner js-home-equalHeight_frame-content\">\n<p class=\"frame_tel\"><a href=\"tel:05017831000\">050-1783-1000</a>（代）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"home-button js-home-equalHeight_button\">\n<li><a href=\"https://mdh.fm/e?kA6030UOBb\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"a-blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span>下関店専用お問い合わせフォーム</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"column_col\">\n<div class=\"toggle_frame\">\n<h4 class=\"frame_heading js-home-equalHeight_frame-heading\">福岡天神店</h4>\n<div class=\"frame_inner js-home-equalHeight_frame-content\">\n<p class=\"frame_tel\"><a href=\"tel:0927128181\">（092）712-8181</a>（代）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"home-button js-home-equalHeight_button\">\n<li><a href=\"https://mdh.fm/e?kA6030UOBB\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"a-blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span>福岡天神店専用お問い合わせフォーム</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"column_col\">\n<div class=\"toggle_frame\">\n<h4 class=\"frame_heading js-home-equalHeight_frame-heading\">高知大丸</h4>\n<div class=\"frame_inner js-home-equalHeight_frame-content\">\n<p class=\"frame_tel\"><a href=\"tel:0888225111\">（088）822-5111</a>（代）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"home-button js-home-equalHeight_button\">\n<li><a href=\"https://mdh.fm/e?kA803S5Xnb\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"a-blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span>高知大丸専用お問い合わせフォーム</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<!--<section class=\"column_col\">\n                            <div class=\"toggle_frame\">\n                              <h4 class=\"frame_heading js-home-equalHeight_frame-heading\">大丸インテリア館「ミュゼ エール」</h4>\n                              <div class=\"frame_inner js-home-equalHeight_frame-content\">\n                                <p class=\"frame_tel\"><a href=\"tel:0788465017\">（078）846-5017</a></p>\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <ul class=\"home-button js-home-equalHeight_button\">\n                              <li><a href=\"https://mdh.fm/e?kA6036SLUp\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"a-blank\"><span>お問い合わせフォーム</span></a></li>\n                            </ul>\n                          </section>--></div>\n<!--<<ul class=\"home-button type-alC\">\n                          <li><a href=\"/yamashina/\" target=\"_blank\"><span>お問い合わせはこちら</span></a></li>\n                        </ul>--></section>\n<section class=\"other_lang\">\n<h3 id=\"anc-01\" class=\"toggle_heading_2\">关于日语以外的咨询／Regarding inquiry except for Japanese／<br />日本語以外でのお問い合わせについて</h3>\n<ul class=\"toggle_note\">\n<li><span class=\"note_mark\">※</span>年底前无休（元旦、1月2日停业）／*Open year round (except for January 1 and 2)／</li>\n<li><span class=\"note_mark\">※</span>年内無休(元日・1月2日は休業)</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"toggle_column_2 js-home-equalHeight js-home-esc-sp-equalHeight\">\n<section class=\"column_col\">\n<div class=\"col_heading js-home-equalHeight_heading\">\n<figure class=\"heading_icon\"><img src=\"/faq/image_new/index_ic01.png\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\n<h4 class=\"heading_title\">如有任何疑问请咨询日本大丸松坂屋百货微信公众号（中文服务）</h4>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col_text js-home-equalHeight_text\">\n<p>If you have any queries, please contact Daimaru Matsuzakaya Department Stores WeChat Official account.(Available in Chinese)</p>\n<p>中国語でのお問い合わせのお客様は大丸松坂屋百貨店WeChat公式アカウントへご連絡ください。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col_frame js-home-equalHeight_frame\">\n<div class=\"frame_inner\">\n<dl class=\"frame_qr\">\n<dt><img src=\"/faq/image_new/index_im01.png\" alt=\"\" /></dt>\n<dd>WeChat ID：dwsbbaihuo</dd>\n</dl>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"column_col\">\n<div class=\"col_heading js-home-equalHeight_heading\">\n<figure class=\"heading_icon\"><img src=\"/faq/image_new/index_ic02.png\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\n<h4 class=\"heading_title\">If you have any queries, please contact Daimaru Matsuzakaya Department Stores Facebook Official account.(Available in English)</h4>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col_text js-home-equalHeight_text\">\n<p>如有任何疑問請咨詢日本大丸松坂屋百貨店Facebook企業號（英語&middot;漢語服務）</p>\n<p>中国語以外のお問い合わせのお客様は大丸松坂屋百貨店Facebook公式アカウントへご連絡ください。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col_frame js-home-equalHeight_frame\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/daimarudps/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"frame_inner\" rel=\"noopener\">\n<dl class=\"frame_qr\">\n<dt><img src=\"/faq/image_new/index_im02.png\" alt=\"\" /></dt>\n<dd>Daimaru Department Stores Global</dd>\n</dl>\n</a></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"toggle_screen js-homeToggle-basic\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"toggle_change js-homeToggle-basic_switch\">\n<h2 class=\"switch_heading\">オンラインストアについて</h2>\n</a>\n<div class=\"toggle_panel js-homeToggle-basic_panel\">\n<div class=\"toggle_inner\">\n<section class=\"toggle_column\">\n<h3 class=\"toggle_heading\"><span>大丸松坂屋オンラインストア</span></h3>\n<div class=\"toggle_column type-alC\">\n<section class=\"toggle_frame\">\n<h4 class=\"frame_heading js-home-equalHeight_frame-heading\">大丸松坂屋オンラインストアに関するお問い合わせ</h4>\n<div class=\"frame_inner js-home-equalHeight_frame-content\">\n<p class=\"frame_tel\"><a href=\"tel:0120917775\">（0120）917-775</a></p>\n<p class=\"frame_text\">受付時間　10時〜20時</p>\n<ul class=\"toggle_note type-frame\">\n<li><span class=\"note_mark\">※</span>年内無休（元日・1月2日は休業）</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<section class=\"column_col\">\n<ul class=\"home-button js-home-equalHeight_button\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.daimaru-matsuzakaya.jp/form/ContactInput\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"a-blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span